Managing Emergency Care zooms into Dispatching Ambulance, Triaging Patient, Diagnosing Condition, Treating Patient, and Discharging Patient, in that sequence.
Emergency Department exhibits Managing Emergency Care.
Triage Nurse handles Triaging Patient.
Emergency Physician handles Diagnosing Condition.
Emergency Physician handles Treating Patient.
Ambulance handles Dispatching Ambulance.
Dispatching Ambulance changes Ambulance from available to dispatched.
Triaging Patient changes Patient from incoming to triaged.
